      <p>
        <s>I wouldn't completely agree with the statement <quote>In America there are no barriers to success</quote>.</s>
        <s>Even if that's exactly what the American <choice><orig>dream</orig><reg>Dream</reg></choice> stands for.</s>
        <s>In my opinion it's an illusion.</s>
        <s>The social system in <name type="geo">America</name> isn't that good.</s>
        <s>There aren't equal rights for women, black people, immigrants, and members of the <choice><abbr>LGBTQ+</abbr><expan>Lesbian Gay Bisexual Transgender Queer</expan></choice> community.</s>
        <s>So this statement <choice><orig>doesnt</orig><reg>doesn't</reg></choice> make sense to me.</s>
      </p>
